<p>
This tutorial comes from 1995&rsquo;s pre-release edition of
<a href='guis/magiccap/magiccapwindows'>Magic Cap for Windows</a>. Unfortunately, 
the collection of screenshots is not complete as a connection to AT&T PersonaLink 
Services could not be made.
</p>


